{"tid":1392554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"塞鐵嘅代價遠比成效大 要塞就塞羅湖","createTime":"2019-07-31T19:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T05:39:09.000Z","uid":181832,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6583f931e730a77b1d42a10fa012311485bb4f92","tid":1392554,"uid":181832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:17:48.000Z","msg":"搞鐵係有用 <br />\n但代價一定遠大過成果<br />\n<br />\n事實上真係失去咗好多民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無撚威脅到正苦<br />\n<br />\n到最後到底呢場塞鐵嘅不合作運動<br />\n係同市民作對定同政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞咗咁多次都無咩作用<br />\n到底係你班番早嘅奴隸想有藉口遲番工射波<br />\n定真心為香港？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要搞就搞羅湖落馬洲 <br />\n搞香港人做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下塞羅湖 搞到支那狗出唔到市區<br />\n運唔到水貨 啲關塞爆人<br />\n中共實同你死過"},{"pid":"c3f57838ab8c2dfe910c9e5a897e6fcac1c943c0","tid":1392554,"uid":290385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74d641303723fa1f399521471b58ff9a584138fc","tid":1392554,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:39:57.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n香港政府笑9你傻仔ja"},{"pid":"966c7f5e12d5ea113886ca37ffc3db721ef609db","tid":1392554,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:45:32.000Z","msg":"［麻煩置頂］而家只剩返 香 港 人 回 合 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7f7618977f0a152c3f7099a8d0ba0704cf04df8","tid":1392554,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f57838ab8c2dfe910c9e5a897e6fcac1c943c0","tid":1392554,"uid":290385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:46:25.000Z","msg":"我留意左你好耐 每到深夜<br />\n就係咁去唔同帶風向po推po"},{"pid":"1407b6833a84b27fd96ddf2ba5fd170cf397c224","tid":1392554,"uid":58841,"like